 href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110712)\">Rev. 4:6-9<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110719\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110719)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110719)\">Rev. 5:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110793\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110793)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110793)\">Rev. 13:1,3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106947\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106947)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106947)\">Prov. 17:14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109910\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109910)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109910)\">Col. 2:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111280\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111280)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111280)\">2 Ne. 28:9,12,15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111192\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111192)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111192)\">2 Ne. 9:28<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109504\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109504)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109504)\">1 Cor. 11:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111678\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111678)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111678)\">Mosiah 18:21-22<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112603\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112603)\">&nbsp;<